Explain about current business of Agri Shop:-
  The current business of the online selling application for the agri shop involves providing a platform for farmers to conveniently purchase agricultural products. 
  The agri shop serves as a supplier of various agricultural items such as seeds, fertilizers, equipment, and other related products
